    "The National Adaptation Plan (NAP) Process will serve as a 10-year blueprint (2020–2030) guiding adaptation planning and implementation, with a review around 2029 and a new framework developed for 2031–2040.": 0,
    "Liberia’s NAP Process (2020–2030) will reduce vulnerability and build adaptive capacity/resilience, and facilitate integration of climate change adaptation into fiscal, regulatory, and development policies, programs, and activities.": 0,
