    "Coastal adaptation strategy: develop and implement coastal zone policy/design/management plan; develop an integrated coastal management plan and early warning system with training; promote disaster risk management and preparedness; rehabilitate and protect wetlands and mangroves; and climate-proof new coastal infrastructure investments.": 0,
    "Coastal adaptation strategy: design and implement a strategic communication action plan to inform and educate the public on climate change-related coastal changes, challenges, and adaptation options.": 0,
    "Energy adaptation strategy: establish and promote a national solar energy program and other energy-efficient lighting technologies, including provision of energy-efficient technologies for schools, public institutions, and households.": 0,
